{"tid":1457080,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你地愈係指責，愈係嬲，就中晒對方計","createTime":"2019-08-12T11:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T13:07:11.000Z","uid":162441,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b7c77c060daa3ea59dc4c04a8a17d72c36c8f92a","tid":1457080,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:13:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>對方就係想我地內訌啊<br />\n藉此黎整散我地</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n去到呢個時候<br />\n唔好因為不忿氣，而責備任何同路人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不分化　不割蓆　事後檢討　下一步再作出改善</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"2eb6fd02f466dc0586a8366c52a7eb7b99405a39","tid":1457080,"uid":9736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:26:28.000Z","msg":"去定留根本唔係重點 重點係依家分化緊！"},{"pid":"4b33edceba5ab32a4d9e7dedce42aa965a4abd64","tid":1457080,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:26:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5d623e88c67dd7503c90838b18b70821a1c03e6c","tid":1457080,"uid":118482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:32:12.000Z","msg":"中計黨散水黨"},{"pid":"5901ff31439169164fc3fc07347318a1f9b4c006","tid":1457080,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:41:34.000Z","msg":"散水黨，中計黨，我咩都信<br />\n<br />\n我信大部分本意都係因為擔心而叫人散水<br />\n<br />\n事實上我地係界分唔到邊啲係人定鬼<br />\n<br />\n唯有信晒大家都係人<br />\n<br />\n毋忘初衷，無論大家做任何手段，都為咗同一目標<br />\n<br />\n外邊愈出呢啲心灰、屌人POST對事情沒有幫助<br />\n<br />\n對家反而睇我地笑話"},{"pid":"4368b87ff3956f7bb3bb50481c805ce505d3acc1","tid":1457080,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:44:02.000Z","msg":"對家最驚係咩?<br />\n因為冇大台都團結到咁多人出黎<br />\n<br />\n佢地拆唔到大台<br />\n就只能用呢啲手段去拆散我地<br />\n我地愈多屌鬼POST，班POPO睇得愈開心<br />\n<br />\n大家要保持一個強心態<br />\n勿要被憤怒去控制你既行動"},{"pid":"10de1a232b4244378c166f2a2f7e0526bbf83b74","tid":1457080,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:49:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10daa4e3e26fd26078d5f4b4dc09b7b167b110ab","tid":1457080,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T11:53:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5547b0478bbbd157ebbc99791500343fed6762aa","tid":1457080,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T12:03:23.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推 勁推推推推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">勿忘721 811</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"81e8915c51f528b359528f397715e6109274af76","tid":1457080,"uid":162441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T13:07:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}